snippet.title: Ultra Foodmess 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A chaotic world trip, 32 characters, multiple game modes and lots of fun! 
These are the words that best define Ultra Foodmess 2.

Your favorite food characters will battle each other in faster and even more dynamic game modes, and now with a Dash action! 

Are you ready to embark on this trip? 
So grab your passports and bring your friends to explode, shoot, push and dodge in this party game created to deliver hours of friendship-ruining fun!
